u} = -\mathbf{F}_{
u \mu})$ is antisymmetric in all frames. Show that the contravariant components are also antisymmetric $(\mathbf{F}^{\mu 
u} = -\mathbf{F}^{
u \mu})$ . Show that symmetry is also coordinate invariant.

